{"ts":"2026-07-13T08:57:49.715Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-7je0"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-533: create/update accept empty --title — required-title contract inconsistent between omitted and empty string"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"pm create --type Task --title \"\" succeeds and persists an empty title, and pm update <id> --title \"\" clears an existing title, while omitting --title on create correctly errors 'Missing required option --title'. Title-less items render meaninglessly in lists and break title-keyed tooling (dedupe is title-prefix based). Fix: treat empty/whitespace-only --title as invalid on both create and update with the same required-option error shape; note extension.name already has a load-bearing .trim() precedent (PR#339–#351 era) — apply the same trim-then-require rule."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["cli","data-integrity","gh-issue","validation"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:57:49.715Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:57:49.715Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":45},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Empty or whitespace-only --title rejected on create and update; error shape matches the missing-required-option error; regression tests; GH-533 closed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"df5a69ef44394b3bdd4a7ec8ea7df73cdee12de9c858254c3926168c58bc329b",